                                                                        EVENT BUBBLING


event bubbling : upward propagation of the events is bubbling.
explanation : In event bubbling, the event starts from the target element (the deepest element that triggered the event) and propagates upwards through its ancestors in the DOM tree.

                                                                        EVENT CAPTURING(EVENT TRICKING)


event capturing : downward propagation for events is event capturing.
explanation: In event capturing, the event starts from the root of the DOM tree and propagates downwards to the target element.

